headline: US oil futures pare losses despite API showing 19M jump in US crude inventories
summary: Investing.com -- U.S. crude oil futures were slightly higher from post-settlement levels Tuesday even as the American Petroleum Institute reported a massive surprise increase in weekly domestic crude inventories.
